'Bless my heart and soul ! cried Mr. Fish . 
And wherever the great people were , there , to be sure , attracted by the kindred sympathy between great souls , was Cute . 
Several voices cried that he was in the circle round Sir Joseph . 
Mr. Fish made way there found him and took him secretly into a window near at hand . 
Not of his own accord . 
He felt that his steps were led in that direction . 
