A public calamity ! I shall make a point of wearing the deepest mourning . 
A most respectable man ! But there is One above . 
We must submit , Mr. Fish . 
We must submit ! What , Alderman ! No word of Putting Down ? Remember , Justice , your high moral boast and pride . 
Come , Alderman ! Balance those scales . 
